catList: Discrete-time Fourier transform. Discrete-time processing of continuous-time signals. Basic communication concepts, modulation, AM, FM, pulse amplitude modulation. Laplace transform, system response. Z-transform. Systems characterized by differential and difference equations. Control systems and feedback. Uncertainty and randomness in signals and systems.
